text.section:
All numbers placed upon the bow of a motorboat subject to this numbering system shall be:
Painted on, or attached to, each side of the bow (i.e. the forward half) of the vessel;
Read from left to right;
And in such position as to provide maximum visibility;
In block letters of good proportion not less than three (3) inches in height;
Have spaces that are equal to the width of a letter other than "I" or a number other than "1" between the letter and the number groupings (Example: KY 1234 A);
Of a color which will contrast with the color of the background (i.e. dark numbers on a light background) and so maintained as to be clearly visible and legible.
